high_descs: Go to the counter that's to the left of the fridge
Grab the knife off of the counter
Turn left and face the cabinets above the counter
Put the knife on the plate in the first cabinet
Grab the plate out of the cabinet
Turn around and head to the round table
Put the plate on the table
anns.task_desc: Putting a plate with a knife on it on the round table

high_descs: Turn left and take one step, then turn right and take two steps, then turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the knife that is on the counter.
Turn around and take one step, then turn right and look up.
Open the cabinet and put the knife on the plate.
Pick up the plate with the knife on it.
Turn around and walk to the table, then turn left to face the table.
Place the plate and knife on the table next to the bread.
anns.task_desc: Set the dishes on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and take one step, turn right for six steps then take another right to face the counter.
Pick up the knife at the back of the counter, under the cabinet.
Turn around for one step, turn right and take one step and stop.
Open the upper cabinet doors and place the knife, standing vertically on the upper left of the plate in the cabinet.
Pick up the plate and the still-standing knife and close the cabinet doors.
Turn around and take seven steps, take a left for one step then turn right to face the table.
Place the plate and knife on the table to the right of the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Get a knife with a plate and put them on the table.
